data.description: Attention, incredible opportunity available to VA buyers with 2.5% assumable Loan!! Welcome home to this spacious and well-maintained two-story home with an attached garage! Boasting 1,976sf of living space, 3 bedrooms, and 2.5 baths. This home features a cozy living room and a separate dining area, perfect for large gatherings and entertaining. Step outside to the backyard and you'll discover a large, covered patio and hot tub overlooking the garden, perfect for relaxing after a long day. Spend your summers enjoying the beautiful Hood Canal with private community beach access just minutes away. This neighborhood provides easy access to nearby trails, shopping, and other amenities. Fresh paint, new flooring, and Rv parking this a must-see!
